OL,3,CSoham killer Ian Huntley died from
OL,4,Cblunt head injury, inquest hears
OL,6,FSoham killer Ian Huntley died as a
OL,7,Fresult of a blunt head injury, an
OL,8,Finquest has heard.
OL,10,FThe 52-year-old died in the Royal
OL,11,FVictoria Infirmary in Newcastle on 7
OL,12,FMarch after he was attacked with a
OL,13,Fmetal bar in a workshop at HMP
OL,14,FFrankland in Durham on 26 February, an
OL,15,Finquest opening hearing was told on
OL,16,FTuesday (14 April).
OL,18,FThe County Durham and Darlington
OL,19,FCoroner Jeremy Chipperfield was
OL,20,Fsitting in Crook, County Durham.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
