OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776255070
OL,3,CSoham killer Ian Huntley died from
OL,4,Cblunt head injury, inquest hears
OL,6,FListed under the name Ian Kevin
OL,7,FHuntley, the inquest opening lasted
OL,8,Fless than five minutes.
OL,10,FCoroner's officer Bradley King read a
OL,11,Fstatement in which he said: "This 52-
OL,12,Fyear-old male was born on January 31
OL,13,Fin 1974 in Grimsby.
OL,15,F"His last employment status and
OL,16,Foccupation is recorded as being a
OL,17,Fprisoner.
OL,19,F"He resided at HMP Frankland.
OL,26,@sD@]OUwD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
