PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776255070
OL,3,CSoham killer Ian Huntley died from
OL,4,Cblunt head injury, inquest hears
OL,6,F"He died on March 7 2026 at the Royal
OL,7,FVictoria Infirmary.
OL,9,F"I understand the circumstances to be
OL,10,Fthat Mr Huntley was struck over the
OL,11,Fhead multiple times by another
OL,12,Fprisoner with an object described as a
OL,13,Fmetal bar.
OL,15,F"The assault left Mr Huntley with
OL,16,Fsignificant head injuries."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUwD@AOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
