FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776255070
OL,3,CSoham killer Ian Huntley died from
OL,4,Cblunt head injury, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe coroner's officer said Home Office
OL,7,FPathologist Dr Jennifer Bolton
OL,8,Fconducted a post mortem on 9 March and
OL,9,Fgave the cause of death as "blunt head
OL,10,Finjury".
OL,12,FHuntley's body was formally identified
OL,13,Fon the day he died.
OL,15,FThe inquest was told that a police
OL,16,Finvestigation was under way and that
OL,17,FAnthony Russell, 43, has been charged
OL,18,Fwith murdering Huntley at the maximum
OL,19,Fsecurity jail.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
