OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776255070
OL,3,CSoham killer Ian Huntley died from
OL,4,Cblunt head injury, inquest hears
OL,6,FMr Chipperfield adjourned the hearing
OL,7,Funtil 27 May when there will have been
OL,8,Fan update in the criminal proceedings.
OL,10,FRussell will attend Newcastle Crown
OL,11,FCourt on 24 April for a pre-trial
OL,12,Fpreparation hearing.
OL,14,FHuntley was serving a life sentence
OL,15,Ffor the 2002 murders of 10-year-olds
OL,16,FHolly Wells and Jessica Chapman.
OL,18,FThe ex-school caretaker killed the
OL,19,Fbest friends after they left a family
OL,20,Fbarbecue to buy sweets in Soham,
OL,21,FCambridgeshire, on 4 August 2002.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
