FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776255070
OL,3,CSoham killer Ian Huntley died from
OL,4,Cblunt head injury, inquest hears
OL,6,FHe dumped their bodies in a ditch 10
OL,7,Fmiles away. They were not found for 13
OL,8,Fdays, despite a search involving
OL,9,Fhundreds of police.
OL,11,FAt the time, Huntley lived with Maxine
OL,12,FCarr, who was a teaching assistant at
OL,13,FHolly and Jessica's primary school.
OL,15,FHe denied murdering the girls but was
OL,16,Fconvicted after a trial at the Old
OL,17,FBailey in 2003. He was jailed for life
OL,18,Fwith a recommended minimum term of 40
OL,19,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
